Truly International announces monthly unaudited turnover for May 2017












Monday, 5 Jun 2017 06:03am EDT June 5 (Reuters) - Truly International Holdings Ltd <0732.HK>:Unaudited net consolidated turnover of group was approximately hk$1,817 million for May 2017.Unaudited net accumulative consolidated turnover for five months ended 31 May 2017 amounted to about hk$9,051 million. 



        Latest Developments forTruly International Holdings Ltd



Truly International says June ‍net consolidated turnover was about HK$1,783 million

Truly International reports qtrly profit attributable of HK$62.4 mln

Truly International expects that consolidated profit attributable for Qtr ended 31 March may significantly decrease by around 70%

Truly International updates on capital increase agreement






